data.description: Greetings to Blue Stone Harbor! This attractive two-story home, nestled in a cul-de-sac, belongs to a coveted Lake Access Community. It boasts a deeded boat slip, four bedrooms, a bonus room, a flexible space, an extra dining area, and a rear deck complete with a pergola for delightful outdoor gatherings. Enjoy the perks of lake living complemented by the convenience of being centrally situated in Cornelius, offering easy access to shopping, dining, and the I-77. Additionally, residents can indulge in neighborhood amenities such as lake access, a clubhouse with a pool, and tennis courts.
